```plantuml
@startuml icoxfog417_karura

actor User
participant "Karura Master App & Client Plugin" as Client
participant "Karura Server" as Server
participant "Model Manager" as ModelManager
participant "Model Builder" as ModelBuilder
participant "Dataset" as Dataset
participant "Field Manager" as FieldManager

User -> Client: Configure ML Task
Client -> Server: POST /train
Server -> ModelManager: Initiate Training
ModelManager -> Dataset: Load Data
Dataset -> FieldManager: Validate & Setup Fields
FieldManager -> Dataset: Return Validated Data
Dataset -> ModelBuilder: Prepare Features
ModelBuilder -> ModelManager: Train Model
ModelManager -> ModelBuilder: Evaluate Model
ModelManager -> Server: Return Training Response
Server -> Client: Training Complete

Client -> Server: POST /predict
Server -> ModelManager: Initiate Prediction
ModelManager -> FieldManager: Load Model & Fields
FieldManager -> Dataset: Prepare Prediction Data
Dataset -> ModelManager: Return Prediction Data
ModelManager -> Server: Return Prediction Result
Server -> Client: Display Prediction

@enduml
```